        ". Thorne, B., Henley, T. . Hermann Ebbinghaus in Connections in the History and Systems of Psychology . Belmont, CA: Wadsworth Cengage Learning.       In 1885, he published his groundbreaking Über das Gedächtnis  in which he described experiments he conducted on himself to describe the processes of ": null
